internal.content: --- title: "report-toolkit API" --- report-toolkit API Here, you'll find documentation for 's public, programmatic API. If you want to use as a library or otherwise embed its functionalities into an app, these docs are for you. Below, you'll find an index of modules comprising the public API. At the time of this writing, the list below _does not_ contain the _entirety_ of this API--but it's enough to get started using as a library. **Hint:** Start with [@report-toolkit/core](/api/modules/report_toolkit_core)! ## Packages - [@report-toolkit/common](/api/modules/report_toolkit_common) - [@report-toolkit/core](/api/modules/report_toolkit_core) - [@report-toolkit/inspector](/api/modules/report-toolkit-inspector) ## Index ### Packages - ["common/diagnostic-report.d"](modules/common_diagnostic_report_d_) - ["transformers/src/index.d"](modules/transformers_src_index_d_) - ["transformers/src/transformer.d"](modules/transformers_src_transformer_d_) - [@report-toolkit/common](modules/report_toolkit_common) - [@report-toolkit/core](modules/report_toolkit_core) - [@report-toolkit/inspector](modules/report_toolkit_inspector)
